#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today’s topic is about solving problems.\n"
"\n"
"Every family has challenges, but working together helps us find calm, good solutions — at home, at school, in the community and online."
msgstr ""
"Isihloko sanamhlanje simalunga nokusombulula ingxaki.\n"
"\n"
"Zonke intsapho zinemicelimngeni, kodwa ukusebenzisana kunye kuyasincedisa sifumane ukuzola, izisombululo ezilungileyo --- ekhaya, esikolweni, ekuhlaleni kunye nakwi-intanethi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How can problem solving help you and your family?"
msgstr "Ukusombulula ingxaki kungakunceda njani wena nosapho lwakho?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is problem solving.\n"
"\n"
"We all know that in life there are times where we face problems, and we all know in a way that when we find ourselves in these situations, it is difficult to think of immediate positive solutions.\n"
"\n"
"Therefore, it is important that when we are facing problems we take a pause, we breathe, keep calm and think of problem-solving skills that we may use."
msgstr ""
"Molweni, nonke. \n"
"\n"
"Isihloko sanamhlanje singokusombulula ingxaki.\n"
"\n"
"Sonke siyayazi ebomini kunamaxesha apho sidibana neengxaki, kwaye sonke siyayazi ngendlela yokuba xa sizifumna sikwezimeko, kunzima ukucinga ngokukhawuleza ngezisombululo ezilungileyo.\n"
"\n"
"Ngoko ke, kubalulekile ukuba xa sidibana neengxaki sime, siphefumle, sihlale sizolile kwaye sicinge ngezakhono esinokuzisebenzisa zokusombulula iingxaki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"As caregivers, we sometimes think we need to fix every problem by ourselves. And teens can think the same! \n"
"\n"
"By involving your teen, you strengthen your relationship as well as their confidence. Together you can overcome anything."
msgstr ""
"Singabazali, ngamanye amaxesha sicinga ukuba kufuneka silungise zonke iingxaki ngokwethu. Kwaye nabantwana abafikisiyo bacinga ngendlela enye!\n"
"\n"
"Ngokubandakanya umntwana wakho ofikisayo, uqinisa ubudlelwane kwakunye nokuzithemba kwabo. Ninonke ningoyisa yonke into."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can problem solving keep your teens safe? It did for @data.characters.media_female_4.name - tap play to hear her story"
msgstr "Ingaba ukusombulula iingxaki kungagcina abantwana bakho abafikisayo bekhuselekile? Yenzekile ku @data.characters.media_female_4.name - cofa dlala uzokuva ibali lakhe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I did not have a good relationship with my daughter. I was always shouting at her, and she was refusing to go to school.\n"
"\n"
"Only when I started spending One-on-One time with her, I realised that she did not want to go to school because she was being bullied at school. We sat down and used the steps of problem solving. We identified the problem, and figured out solutions together: “What can I do as a parent so you can attend school and feel safe?”\n"
"\n"
"We agreed I would go talk to the teacher to find a way forward. We really found the solutions together, and we are closer now."
msgstr ""
"Bendingenabo ubudlelwane ubuhle kunye nentombi yam. Bendisoloko ngalo lonke ixesha ndimngxolisa, kwaye bengafuni ukuya ukuya esikolweni. \n"
"\n"
"Kuphela xa ndaqalisa ukuchitha ixesha Lomnye Nomnye kunye naye, ndaye ndaqonda ukuba engafuni nje ukuya esikolweni uyaxhatshazwa esikolweni. Siye sahlala phantsi sasebenzisa amanyathelo okusombulula ingxaki. Siyibonile ingxaki, kwaye sakhangela izisombululo kunye: \"Yintoni endingayenza njengomzali ukwenzela ukwazi ukuya esikolweni kwaye uzive ukhuselekile?\"\n"
"\n"
"Sivumelene ukuba ndizakuya ku titshala ukufumana indlela eya phambili. Siye sazifumana ngokwenene izisombululo kunye, kwaye sisondelene ngoku."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_15.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Problem-solving together is an important skill for every family. Let’s see how @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name and @data.characters.f2_son_15.name handle a problem calmly and find a plan together."
msgstr "Ukusombulula ingxaki kunye sisakhono esibalulekileyo kusapho lonke. Masibone ukuba u@data.characters.f2_grandmother.name kunye no @data.characters.f2_son_15.name bayiphatha njani ingxaki ngokuzolileyo kwaye bafumane icebo kunye."

#. type=data_list
#. The string _@data.characters.f2_grandmother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "_@data.characters.f2_grandmother.name is coming home from work._"
msgstr "_@data.characters.f2_grandmother.name ubuya emsebenzini._"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_15.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_son_15.name! Look at all those dishes, why did you not wash those like we agreed!"
msgstr "@data.characters.f2_son_15.name! Jonga kuzo zonke ezazitya, kutheni ungazivasanga njengoba besivumelene!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name… should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sorry, @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name… I can explain, there is this guy from my class, on WhatsApp he…"
msgstr "Uxolo, @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name… Ndingacacisa, kukhona lomfana eklasini yam, kuWhatsApp u…"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "(_thinking_): Let me take a pause… just breathe…"
msgstr "(_ecinga_): Makhe ndiphumle... ukuphefumla nje…"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am sorry, @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name."
msgstr "Ndiyaxolisa, @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now tell me, what happened on WhatsApp?"
msgstr "Ngoku ndixelele, yintoni eyenzekileyo ku WhatApp?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This boy in class shared a video of me in a WhatsApp group, and now everyone is making fun of me."
msgstr "Le nkwenkwe yabelane ngevidiyo yam kwiqumrhu lika-Whatsapp, kwaye wonke umntu ngoku uhlekisa ngam."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_15.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am sorry to hear that, but I am glad you told me, @data.characters.f2_son_15.name. It does not mean you can leave your chores. After we speak, you need to do the dishes so I can make dinner. But first, what do you think we should do about the bully problem?"
msgstr "Ndiyaxolisa ukuyiva lonto, kodwa ndiyavuya undixelele, @data.characters.f2_son_15.name. Loo nto ayithethi ukuba uyeke umsebenzi wakho. Emva kokuba sithethile, kumele uvase izitya ndizokwazi ukwenza isidlo sangokuhlwa. Kodwa kuqala, ucinga ukuba sifanele senze ntoni ngengxaki yokuxhatshazwa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He makes me so angry, I just want to hit him. Or maybe I should tell my teacher?"
msgstr "Undenza ndibenomsindo kakhulu, ndifuna nje ukumbetha. Okanye ndingaxelela utitshala wam?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hmm… What do you think will happen if you hit him? And if you tell your teacher?"
msgstr "Hmm... Ucinga ukuba yintoni enokwenzeka xa umbethile? Kwaye ukuba uxelele utitshala wakho?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I don’t know. If I hit him we may get into a big fight and I could get hurt or get into trouble at school. But if I tell my teacher they may call me a snitch… Maybe you could talk to the teacher?"
msgstr "Andiyazi. Ukuba ndiyambetha singangena emlweni omkhulu kwaye ndingonzakala okanye ndibesengxakini esikolweni. Kodwa ukuba ndixelela utitshala wam bangandibiza ngokuba ndiyimpimpi... Mhlawumbi ungathetha notitshala wam?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That sounds like a good idea. I could also go talk to his parents if you want me to."
msgstr "Ivakala ngathi ngumbono omhle lowo. Ndingaya ndiyokuthetha nabazali bakhe ukuba uyafuna ndiye."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name, please don’t! Maybe I can skip school tomorrow instead?"
msgstr "Hayi @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name, ndiyakucela sukuya. Mhlawumbi endaweni yoko ndingangayi esikolweni ngomso?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"No, Thabo — you can’t miss school. \n"
"I have an idea! Let’s practise how you might reply if classmates tease you. Do you want to try ignoring it or making a small joke?"
msgstr ""
"Hayi, Thabo - awukwazi ukuphosa isikolo.\n"
"Ndinombono! Masiziqhelanise ukuba ungabaphendula njani ukuba abantwana ofunda nabo bayakugezela. Ufuna ukuzama ungayihoyi okanye wenze isiqhulo esincinci?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Maybe I’ll just say, “Don’t worry, I was testing gravity — it still works!”"
msgstr "Mhlawumbi ndingathi, \"Sukukhathazeka, bendisavavanya umhlaba - isasebenza!”"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Haha! That’s good! Remember, keeping calm or laughing along takes away their power."
msgstr "Haha! Kulungile! Khumbula, ukungcina uzolile okanye uhleka kunye kususa amandla abo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "_A week later…_"
msgstr "_Emva kweveki..._"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How are things going at school now?"
msgstr "Zihamba njani izinto ngoku esikolweni?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is going better, the boy deleted the video from the WhatsApp group chat. But he is still being really mean to me."
msgstr "Zihamba ngcono, inkwenkwe iyicimile ividiyo kwiqumrhu lika-Whatsapp lokuncokola. Kodwa usandicaphukisa."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_15.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I am sorry to hear that, @data.characters.f2_son_15.name. I will be speaking to your teacher tomorrow — your school knows how to handle this safely.\n"
"If that does not work, we will try something else."
msgstr ""
"Ndiyaxolisa ukuyiva lonto, @data.characters.f2_son_15.name. Ndizakuthetha notitshala wakho ngomso - isikolo sakho siyayazi singayiphatha njani lento ngokukhuselekileyo.\n"
"Ukuba ayisebenzi, sizakuzama enye into."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, thank you, @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name. At least I know you are on my side."
msgstr "Ewe, enkosi, @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name. Noko ndiyayazi usecaleni kwam."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When you face a problem, take a few deep breaths to help you stay calm. \n"
"Then, try to handle the problem using these four steps!"
msgstr ""
"Xa ujongene nengxaki, tsala umoya kambalwa ukukunceda uhlale uzolile.\n"
"Emva koko, zama ukulungisa ingxaki usebenzisa lamanyathelo mane!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "KNOW IT"
msgstr "YAZI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Identify the problem."
msgstr "Fumanisa ingxaki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SOLVE IT"
msgstr "YISOMBULULE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Think of possible solutions and what would happen if we used them."
msgstr "Cinga ngezisombululo ezinokubakho nokuthi kungenzeka ntoni ukuba sinokuzisebenzisa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "TRY IT"
msgstr "YIZAME"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Choose a solution and try it out."
msgstr "Khetha isisombululo uze usizame."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "TEST IT"
msgstr "SIVAVANYE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Did it work? Great! If it did not work, then try another solution."
msgstr "Ngaba sisebenzile? Kulunge kakhulu! Ukuba asikhange sisebenze, khawuzame esinye isisombululo."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Now let’s try problem-solving ourselves.\n"
"Imagine that @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name got a phone as a gift from a boy, and her mother, @data.characters.f1_mother.name, feels worried about it."
msgstr ""
"Ngoku masizame isisombululo sengxaki ngokwethu.\n"
"Ibanombono u@data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name efumene ifowuni njengesipho enkwenkweni, kwaye umama wakhe u@data.characters.f1_mother.name, uziva ekhathazekile ngalonto."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What could @data.characters.f1_mother.name do to handle the situation when @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name got a phone from a boy?"
msgstr "Yintoni anokuyenza u@data.characters.f1_mother.name ukumelana nesimo xa u@data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name efumana ifowuni esuka enkwenkweni?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ground @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name for a month"
msgstr "Mohlwaye u@data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name kangangenyanga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Return the phone and save up together to buy a new one"
msgstr "Buyisela ifowuni kwaye songe sobabini sizothenga entsha"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk to @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name about safe sex"
msgstr "Thetha no@data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name ngokhuseleko kwezesondo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name’s should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Listen to @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name’s side of the story"
msgstr "Mamela ku@data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name icala le bali"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Take a deep breath before reacting"
msgstr "Phefumla nzulu ngaphambi kokuba wenze"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That didn’t work... Let's try something else."
msgstr "Loo nto ayikhange isebenze... Makhe sizame enye into."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You cannot go out for the next month"
msgstr "Awuzuphuma kulenyanga izayo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Uuugh… that’s so unfair, I did not do anything wrong!"
msgstr "Uuugh... ayilunganga lonto, Andenzanga nto embi!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This is a great option! \n"
"\n"
"Parenting teens is really hard. Often there are no simple and easy solutions, but now @data.characters.f1_mother.name learned she can talk to her daughter about these things."
msgstr ""
"Yindlela elungileyo kakhulu!\n"
"\n"
"Ukuba ngumzali ebantwaneni abafikisayo kunzima nyhani. Kusoloko kungekho sisombululo sicacileyo nesilula, kodwa ngoku u@data.characters.f1_mother.name ufunde ukuba angathetha nentombi yakhe ngezizinto."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am not trying to accuse your friend or be jealous. I am worried that when someone gives a gift it is hard to say 'no' when they ask something in return – like sex. If you want to have a phone, we will save up together so you can make your own decisions without owing him anything."
msgstr "Andizami kutyhola umhlobo wakho okanye ukuba nomona. Ndikhathazwa kukuba xa umntu ekuphe isipho kunzima ukuthi ‘hayi’ xa efuna ukubhatalwa – njengokwabelana ngesondo. Ukuba ufuna ukuba nefowuni, siza konga sobabini ukuze ukwazi ukwenza izigqibo zakho ngaphandle kokumtyala into ethile."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That makes sense, thank you, @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name."
msgstr "Iyavakala, enkosi, @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This makes me realise we should talk about boyfriends and protecting yourself. Many teens your age get pregnant or become HIV positive. Let’s go to the clinic so you can talk with the nurse to learn how you can stay safe."
msgstr "Oku kwenza ndiqonde ukuba simele sithethe ngamakhwenkwe nokuzikhusela. Abantwana abasafikisayo abaninzi abalingana nawe bayakhulelwa okanye babe ne- ngculaza (HIV). Masiye ekliniki ukuze uthethe nomongikazi ukuze ubone indlela onokuhlala ngayo ukhuselekile."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, thank you, @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name."
msgstr "Kulungile, enkosi, @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Please tell me your side of the story. I am here to listen."
msgstr "Ndicela undixelela elakho icala lebali. Ndilapha ukumamela."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay… I can explain. He said it was just a gift."
msgstr "Kulungile…Ndingacacisa. Utshilo yena ukuba sisipho nje."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This is a great option! \n"
"\n"
"Parenting teens is really hard. Often there are no simple and easy solutions, but now @data.characters.f1_mother.name learned she can talk to her daughter about these things.\n"
"\n"
"Before, she worried alone, now they can come up with solutions together!"
msgstr ""
"Yindlela elungileyo!\n"
"\n"
"Ukuba ngumzali ebantwaneni abafikisayo kunzima nyhani. Kusoloko kungekho ndlela ilula necacileyo yokusombulula, kodwa ngoku@data.characters.f1_mother.name ufunde ukuba angathetha nentombi yakhe ngezi zinto.\n"
"\n"
"Ngaphambili, ebekhathazeka eyedwa, ngoku banokuza nezisombululo bebobabini!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now that I have had a moment to calm down, let’s talk. How did you get this phone?"
msgstr "Njengokuba ngoku ndibenomzuzu wokwehlisa umoya, singathetha. Uyifumene njani le foni?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He gave it to me after school. I didn’t want to start a fight."
msgstr "Uye wandinika emva kokuphuma kwesikolo. Andifunanga ukuqala umlo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When something bad happens, we often get upset and blame. But what our teens really need is someone to help find solutions together. \n"
"\n"
"Listen to them, accept how they see and feel things, and thank them for trusting you.\n"
"\n"
"Teaching your teen how to deal with problems will help them for the rest of their lives. What a gift!"
msgstr ""
"Xa kusenzeka into embi, amaxesha amaninzi siye sikhathazeke siphinde sisole. Kodwa okona kufunwa ngabantwana bethu abafikisayo ngumntu onokubanceda bafumane isisombululo bekunye.\n"
"\n"
"Bamamele, wamnkele indlela ababona ngayo nabaziva ngayo izinto, ubabulele ngokuba bekuthemba.\n"
"\n"
"Ukufundisa abantwana bakho abafikisayo ngokuqubisana neengxaki kunganceda ubomi babo bonke. Eso sipho!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Here are some examples of problems other caregivers solved with their teens:**\n"
"\n"
"- My teenager does not want to go to school\n"
"- My teenager is on their phone too much\n"
"- I am worried my teenager will get pregnant or will get someone pregnant\n"
"- I am worried about what my teen does online\n"
"- My teenager is hanging out with bad friends"
msgstr ""
"**Nantsi eminye imizekelo yeengxaki ezisonjululwe ngabanye abazali kunye nabantwana babo abafikisayo:**\n"
"\n"
"- Umntwana wam ofikisayo akafuni ukuya esikolweni\n"
"- Umntwana wam ofikisayo ubasefowunini kakhulu.\n"
"- Ndinexhala lokuba umntwana wam ofikisayo angakhulelwa okanye akhulelise umntu\n"
"- Ndinexhala ngezinto ezenziwa ngumntwana wam ofikisayo kumakhasi onxibelelwano\n"
"- Umntwana wam ofikisayo uhlala nabahlobo abangalunganga"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Your home activity this week is to teach your teenagers the steps for problem-solving and use them together when a problem comes up."
msgstr "Umsebenzi wakho wasekhaya kuleveki kukufundisa umntwana wakho ofikisayo ngendlela zokusombulula ingxaki aphinde azisebenzise zonke xa iingxaki zifika."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember to use the four steps of problem-solving:** \n"
"💭 Step 1: KNOW IT (identify problem)\n"
"📋 Step 2: SOLVE IT (identify solutions) \n"
"⚒️ Step 3: TRY IT (try one) \n"
"🎯 Step 4: TEST IT (try another solution if this one did not work)"
msgstr ""
"**Khumbula ukusebenzisa amanyathelo amane ukusombulula ingxaki:**\n"
"💭 Inyathelo 1: YAZI (chonga ingxaki)\n"
"📋 Inyathelo 2: YISOMBULULE (chonga isisombululo)\n"
"⚒️ Inyathelo 3: YIZAME (zama enye)\n"
"🎯 Inyathelo 4: YIVAVANYE (zama esinye isisombululo ukuba le ayisebenzi)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you solve one problem together with your teen this week - using the four steps?"
msgstr "Ningasombulula ingxaki enye nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kuleveki - usebenzisa indlela ezine?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Working together with your teen will bring so many good outcomes for you both."
msgstr "Kulungile! Ukusebenzisana nomntwana wakho ofikisayo kungazisa iziphumo ezininzi ezihle kuni nobabini."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try it out with a ‘small’ problem that may come up, so you can see how it works before tackling a bigger challenge."
msgstr "Ungayenza! Yizame ngengxaki 'encinci' enokuvela, uzokwazi ukubona ukuba isebenza njani ngaphambi kokuba uqubisane nengxaki enkulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. Just remember that when a situation feels overwhelming, it can really help to use the four steps of problem solving with your teen to break the problem down."
msgstr "Kulungile. Ukhumbule ke xa imeko ibonakala ikongamele, kungakunceda ukusebenzisa indlela ezine zokusombulula ingxaki nomntwana wakho ofikisayo ukohlulahlula ingxaki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"We all have problems, but they don’t define us! You can choose to address challenges and try different solutions together with your teen. \n"
"This shows your teen that they are never alone and gives them a key skill to use at home, with friends, and for life!"
msgstr ""
"Sonke sinengxaki, kodwa azichazi ubuthina! Ungakhetha ukuchaza imiceli mingeni uzame izisombululo ezahlukeneyo nomntwana wakho ofikisayo.\n"
"Oku kubonisa ukuba umntwana wakho ofikisayo akayedwa kuphinde kubanike isakhono esingundoqo abanokusisebenzisa ekhaya, nezihlobo, nasebomini!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_son_2.name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you make an impact on your community with these skills? Hear @data.characters.media_son_2.name's story"
msgstr "Ungenza igalelo ekuhlaleni ngezizakhono? Mamela ibali lika@data.characters.media_son_2.name"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When my father introduced the problem-solving steps to me, it helped me with my family, but it also helped me with my friends.\n"
"\n"
"I told my friends about the steps, and now when we are arguing we sit down and everyone comes up with solutions. We then look for the negatives and positives of each solution, and we agree “okay let’s try this one.”\n"
"\n"
"My friends even took it to their own homes, and it is helping with their families as well!\n"
"\n"
"It is great when others listen to you and accept your ideas even though you are young. We can all bring that harmony with our friends and family."
msgstr ""
"Xa utata wam wayendixelela ngamanyathelo okusombulula ingxaki, yandinceda nosapho lwam, yaphinda yandinceda nakwizihlobo zam.\n"
"\n"
"Ndizixelele izihlobo zam ngalamanyathelo, ngoku xa siphikisana sihlala phantsi wonke umntu aze nezisombululo. Siye sijonge okuhle nokubi kwisisombululo ngasinye, sivumelane \" kulungile masizame esi\"\n"
"\n"
"Izihlobo zam ziye lento zayithatha ukuyenza emakhayeni abo, kwaye iyazinceda iintsapho zabo nazo!\n"
"\n"
"Kuhle xa abanye bekumamela kwaye bazamkele izimvo zakho nokuba umncinci. Singayenza imvisiswano nezihlobo kunye nentsapho zethu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉"
msgstr "Wenze kakuhle ngokuthatha ixesha lesiqu sakho namhlanje. 🎉"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr "Nali ushicilelo olufutshane elizokunceda wehlise ngaphambi kokuba uhambe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When everything feels like it is falling apart And you can't help but raise your voice When all the frustrations are beginning to start Remember that you have a choice\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"You can take pause, you can count to 10 Play a game or do something fun You can phone a friend, someone to confide in Remember you're not the only one\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more Because I really couldn't love you more"
msgstr ""
"Xa yonke into ivakala ingathi iyamoshakala Kwaye awukwazi ukuzinceda uvele unyuse ilizwi Xa zonke iinzingo ziqala Khumbula ukuba ungenza ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sehlise kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba andinakuthanda ngakumbi\n"
"\n"
"Yima, ungabala uyokutsho ku 10 Dlala umdlalo okanye wenze into emnandi Ungafowunela umhlobo, umntu onokumchazela ingxaki Khumbula ayinguwe wedwa\n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsala umoya kancinci Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsala umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi \n"
"\n"
"Makhe sime kancinci Tsalaa umoya Khumbula konke esino kubulela ngako Makhe sime Tsalaa umoya kancinci Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi Kuba bendingenokuthanda ngakumbi"

